<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ901221-0072</DOCNO><DOCID>901221-0072.</DOCID><HL>   Sunshine Mining Unit's Venture</HL><DATE>12/21/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   SSC MLRC</CO><IN>DIVERSIFIED MINING (MNG)</IN><LP>   DALLAS -- Sunshine Mining Co. said a subsidiary formed ajoint venture with a subsidiary of Mallon Resources Corp. andRed Rock Ventures Inc., to explore for gold in the GuanacasteProvince of Costa Rica.   Pending the analysis of results from a 36-hole drillingprogram, Sunshine Mining has the option to acquire a 50%interest in and become manager of the venture. If Sunshinechooses to proceed, Mallon will retain a 35% interest in theproject and Red Rock Ventures will retain a 15% stake.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>